election_record.label: Connecticut 1824 State Senate

overview.note: Asa Bacon received 4 votes as Asa Bacon, Jr.
Orange Merwin received 2 votes as Origen Merwin.
Christopher Manwarring received 2 votes as Charles Manwarring and 1 vote as Chester Manwarring.
Elijah Hubbard received 2 votes as Elijah Hibbard.
Nathaniel Terry received 2 votes as Nathaniel Perry.
John S. Peters received 1 vote as John T. Peters.
Roger M. Sherman received 1 vote as Roger S. Sherman.
Two unknown candidates received an unknown number of votes.

sub_unit.note: Seth P. Beers received 1 vote as Seth T. Beers.
